 Note that they seem to be all talking about Fusion reactors, but exactly the same points can be said about Breeder reactors. Hence the ban of breeders is a false solution to the wrong problem. The problem isn't Pu proliferation, it's weapons &amp; war and long past time the protestors saw it.<br>
<br>
YaleS submitted:<br>
&gt;<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Fusion reactors can be used as fission breeders...<br>
&gt;Any breeder is a large proliferation hazard and would have<br>
to be in a secure area with close government oversight....<br>
&gt;Even pure fusion has a significant proliferation hazard in that a rogue country or reactor operator could slip 238U in the blanket and breed plutonium. This potential proliferation hazard of a pure fusion reactor has received very little attention....<br>
&gt;Dr. Wallace Manheimer <br>
Senior Scientist for Fundamental Plasma Processes <br>
Naval Research Laboratory <br>
Washington DC</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
The point is to ban weapons research, not science &amp; energy research.<br>
Perhaps more likely to sway the majority of the populace to accept a worldwide nuclear technology authority than to ban all the necessary sciences &amp; technologies which could lead to proliferation.<br>
<br>
A mysterious stranger known only as &quot;X&quot; wrote (4/20/02)<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> &gt; Let's look at all of these reasons:<br>
&gt; 1). as projectorion once said, what's the difference between a rocket and a missile, what's its pointing at. The same airplanes that fly people across the ocean can deliver thousands of pounds of bombs both conventional and nuclear. If you're opposed to proliferation, then you must oppose:<br>
&gt;<br>
&gt; nuclear physics: the basics of nuclear power<br>
&gt; aircraft: a form of transportation for bombs<br>
&gt; rockets: another delivery system<br>
&gt; radiation theropy: can't have anyone making dirty nukes can we<br>
astronomy: we found out about nuclear fusion by first observing the stars<br>
&gt; education: high school drop-outs can not make a bomb, so we must dumb down everyone<br>
